Layout/ClassStructure.description:
Description

Enforces a configured order of definitions within a class body.
Layout/ClassStructure.option:
This rule supports the following parameters in your configuration:

Categories: {'module_inclusion': ['include', 'prepend', 'extend']} (type: dict)
ExpectedOrder: ['module_inclusion', 'constants', 'public_class_methods', 'initializer', 'public_methods', 'protected_methods', 'private_methods'] (type: list)
